'''cholesterol'''

# {{biochemistry}} A [[sterol]] [[lipid]] [[synthesize]]d by the [[liver]] and transported in the [[bloodstream]] to the membranes of all [[animal]] [[cell]]s; it plays a central role in many [[biochemical]] processes and, as a [[lipoprotein]] that coats the [[wall]]s of [[blood vessel]]s, is [[associated]] with [[cardiovascular]] [[disease]].

